creator: limber.
descriptionHtml:
limber connects you with the best hospitality workers in your area. The app allows you to browse CVs with a difference – all containing ratings from other local businesses. On limber, you can cover shifts, staff events or find your next permanent hire.

In Bristol alone, there are 2000 workers signed up to use the platform. All looking to pick up extra work or find their next challenge.

Sign up now. It's free!
